#MEM id=form-cro source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Marketing/rio/skills/marketing-and-growth/form-cro/SKILL.md savings=1%
M||tx|---
M||name|form-cro
M||desc|>-
M||tx|When the us wants to op any form that is NOT signup/registration — inc lead capture forms, contact forms, demo request forms, application forms, survey forms, or checkout forms. Also use when the us mentions "form op," "lead form conversions," "form friction," "form fields," "form completion rate," "contact form," "nobody fills out our form," "form abandonment," "too many fields," "demo request form," or "lead form isn't converting." Use this for any non-signup form that captures information. For signup/registration forms, see signup-flow-cro. For popups containing forms, see popup-cro.
M||vers|1.0.0
M||plat|[]
M||meta|
M||herm|
M||tags|[paid-ad, meta, tiktok, roas, conversion, retargeting, cpm, mk]
M||vers|1.1.0
